To make the drink rimmer, mix sugar, Diamond Crystal(R) Fine Sea Salt, and spice blend on a small saucer. Pour caramel sauce on another small saucer. Dip the rim of a mug or heatproof glass into the caramel sauce, evenly coating the rim. Then, dip into the rimmer mixture. Heat the apple cider and caramel candy in a small saucepan over medium-low heat. Stir frequently until candies have melted. Ladle hot caramel apple cider into the spice-rimmed mug.